posts.post_title: FS T206 Sweeny Miscut and front ink shift
posts.post_content:
I am considering selling this T206 Sweeney. The card has a nice miscut on the back, and also has an ink shift on the front, and a wetsheet piedmont transfer front. 

Because of the ink shift... part of another cards green ink is shown on the left front of the card.

Before I consign to an auction house I thought I would post on the BST. Please email me your offer if you are interested.
